#: ../develop/addons/schema-driven-forms/intro.rst:35
msgid "This manual will show you how to use *z3c.form* in a Plone context. It will use tools and patterns that are consistent with those used for Dexterity development, as shown in the :doc:`Dexterity developer manual </external/plone.app.dexterity/docs/index>`, but the information contained herein is not Dexterity specific. Note that Dexterityâs standard add and edit forms are all based on *z3c.form*."
