#: ../develop/plone-coredev/plips.rst:7
msgid "A PLIP is a Plone Improvement Proposal. It is a change to a Plone package that would affect everyone. PLIPs go through a different process than bug fixes because of their broad reaching effect. The Plone 4.x Framework Team reviews all PLIPs to be sure that itâs in the best interest of the broader community to be implemented and that it is of high quality."
